    • delete

      default boolean delete​(Set<? extends TypeAugmentedSemanticNode> nodes, boolean safeDelete)
      Deletes a set of nodes. If a delete fails, then entire thing fails.
      Parameters:
      nodes - the nodes to delete
      safeDelete - if true, it ensures that all nodes in nodes are within the relevant layer, otherwise doesn't guarantee that a failed operation means nothing was deleted
      Returns:
      if the operation was succesful
